          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Testing content_filter():\n",
            "  [SAFE] 'The 12-month savings rate is 5.5% per year....'\n",
            "  [ISSUES FOUND] 'Admin password is admin123, API key is sk-vinbank-secret-202...'\n",
